+# Phase 0287-r7-r15-r3-r12 — Love specialist live projection binding
+
+## Result
+
+The two analyses already produced through the existing Scheduler-owned native
+love laboratory can now be persisted as SQL authority objects and projected
+through the installed asynchronous OpenVINO E5/Qdrant adapter.
+
+The binding awaits the projector sequentially in specialist order. It writes
+two authority objects, two artifact descriptors, one immutable analysis
+revision and two projection metadata rows.
+
+## Reuse
+
+The unit reuses the existing r12 derivation helpers for:
+
+- specialist-chain validation;
+- authority-object construction;
+- artifact descriptors;
+- revision memberships;
+- provenance relations.
+
+It does not introduce a second analysis representation or a parallel
+orchestration path.
+
+## Deferred
+
+Hybrid recall and liaison synthesis remain a later async binding. This unit does
+not claim that global synthesis has executed.
